AMENDMENTS TO LB1216
Introduced by Education.
1 1. On page 2, strike lines 12 through 17 and insert the following
2 new subdivision:
3 "(2)(a) The director shall offer and make available educational
4 services and educational programming to any person committed to the
5 department who is under twenty-one years of age and who has not
6 previously earned a high school diploma or diploma of high school
7 equivalency. The director shall ensure special education services are
8 provided as required by state and federal law. Nothing in this subsection
9 requires participation by any person committed to the department in
10 educational services or educational programming except to the extent
11 necessary to provide services required by law.".
